  "content_html": "<p>काठमाडौँ- आज दशैंको पहिलो दिन घटस्थापना सम्पन्न भएको छ। घरघरमा जमरा राखिने परम्पराअनुसार काठमाडौँको बसन्तपुरस्थित दशैंघरमा पनि बिहान जौ छरेर जमरा राखिएको हो।</p>\n<p>घटस्थापनाको क्रममा मंगल धुन बजाउँदै बढाइँ गरेको थियो। पूजाकोठा वा दशैंघरमा विधिपूर्वक दियो, कलश र गणेश स्थापना गरी वैदिक विधिपूर्वक शक्तिकी अधिष्ठात्री दुर्गा देवीको आह्वान गरी पूजा आरम्भ गरिन्छ।</p>\n<p>नवरात्रको पहिलो दिन बिहानै नित्यकर्म पूरा गरी नजिकको नदी वा चोखो स्थलबाट बालुवा वा माटो ल्याइ गाईको गोबरले लिप्पोपत गरिएको पूजाकोठा अथवा दशैंघरमा जौ रोपिन्छ।</p>\n<p>जौको पहेँलो अंकुरण अर्थात् जमरा दुर्गा देवीको प्रिय वस्तु मानिन्छ र यसलाई विजयादशमीको दिन टीका प्रसादसँगै ग्रहण गरिन्छ। पहेँलो जमरालाई समृद्धिको प्रतीक पनि मानिन्छ। घटस्थापनासँगै नवरात्र सुरु हुन्छ।<img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096906\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094653/jamara.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096905\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094653/jamara-pic.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096903\" height=\"1621\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094415/Jamara_dashain_ghar-bashantapur.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096902\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094414/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur11.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096901\" height=\"1379\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094413/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur10.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096900\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094412/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur9.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096899\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094357/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur8.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096898\" height=\"1453\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094356/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur6.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096897\" height=\"1482\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094355/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur5.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096896\" height=\"1348\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094354/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur4.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096895\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094353/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur3.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096894\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094257/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur2.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096893\" height=\"1412\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094257/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur1.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096892\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094256/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur_jamara.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096891\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094255/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096890\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22094254/Ghatisthapana_Basantapur-7.jpg\" width=\"2048\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
